data.description: Nestled in the coveted Wildhorse neighborhood, this adorable one-story home is a paradigm of comfort, and convenience . Ideal for families, those seeking serenity, or individuals requiring mobility-friendly amenities, it features 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms plus a study! It is thoughtfully designed with an open floor plan that enhances the sense of flow throughout the living, dining and kitchen areas. This layout, combined with ample natural light, fosters a warm and inviting atmosphere that's perfect for entertaining or simply relaxing. The kitchen boasts modern stainless steel appliances, cabinet storage and a lovely island. The owner's suite offers a tranquil retreat with its private ensuite bathroom, and the additional bedrooms provide versatile space and walk in closets for family, guests, or to use as a secondary home office!  This home sits on a corner lot includes an attached two-car garage, mature trees for privacy and shade and a privacy fence surrounding a spacious backyard, complete with a covered patio!  Residents of the Wildhorse neighborhood benefit from exclusive amenities such as a community pool, park/playground, sports courts and scenic jogging trails. Situated within the Northside Independent School District (NISD), this gem is within a few minutes to the Elementary School. With its close proximity to parks, shopping and dining, this home skillfully combines practicality with charm, offering a beautifully designed, accessible, and comfortable living space that truly stands out. Don't miss out! Come view your new home today!
